  "changelog": "\n## Version 2.1.0\n* Added mouse hover sound support with a customizable delay in the settings panel.\n* Implemented official support for web browser navigation (Browse Mode) in NVDA 2025.1+, with full backward compatibility for older versions.\n* Fixed audio queueing and freezing delays when rapidly navigating large folders using a 60ms debounce mechanism.\n* Fixed audio muting issues on dynamic elements like visited links and checkboxes.\n* Filtered out background structural elements to prevent spammy noise during mouse movement.\n* Updated Ukrainian and Vietnamese translations.\n",
